# AI Models Reference

## Environment Variables

API keys are in the root project `.env` - use dotenv to access:
- `OPENAI_API_KEY` - OpenAI (GPT-4, DALL-E)
- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` - Anthropic (Claude)
- `MESHY_API_KEY` - Meshy.ai (3D generation)

