## Meshy.ai - 3D Generation

Use **Meshy.ai** for all 3D asset generation in HyperForge.

**See full documentation**: `.cursor/rules/meshy.mdc`

### Meshy AI Model Versions

| Model | Recommended For |
|-------|-----------------|
| `meshy-4` | Image-to-3D (stable) |
| `meshy-5` | Image-to-3D, Retexture (improved geometry) |
| `meshy-6` | Text-to-3D (latest, best quality) |
| `latest` | Always newest (currently Meshy-6) |

### Meshy API Capabilities

| Feature | API Version | Description |
|---------|-------------|-------------|
| Image-to-3D | v1 | Convert images to 3D models |
| Text-to-3D | v2 | Generate 3D from text prompts (two-stage) |
| Retexture | v1 | Apply new textures to models |
| Rigging | v1 | Add skeleton + animations |

