### Polycount Guidelines (Three.js Web MMO)

| Asset Class | Triangles | Examples |
|-------------|-----------|----------|
| Small Props | 500 - 2,000 | coins, potions, keys |
| Medium Props | 2,000 - 5,000 | weapons, barrels |
| Large Props | 5,000 - 10,000 | trees, statues |
| NPCs | 2,000 - 10,000 | characters, monsters |
| Buildings | 5,000 - 50,000 | houses to castles |

**Max per mesh**: 100,000 triangles for web performance